{"tid":159921,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（JUPAS）揀科咪亂來","createTime":"2017-03-17T10:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T11:00:46.000Z","uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f02be56a5cdddfdcf872d9587018ffd2caab1aa","tid":159921,"uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:50:50.000Z","msg":"考得差，入唔到U，唔使愁，千其唔好咁睇唔開去鯨大，或者去外國讀埋啲野雞大學，尤其是台灣私校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登仔追捧I大係有原因嘅（利申：非HD ASSO出身，不過身邊好多同學都係通過咁入番大學）<br />\n首先，唔好咁大想頭，醫生律師同你無緣架喇，不過香港好多好工，特別係建築，甚至係藥劑，HD ASSO都有得讀，出到來仲好過啲讀垃圾科嘅虛榮名牌大學生，更唔好講班鯨魚樹人仔<br />\n再者，我見過嘅HD ASSO仔，九成都上到大學，仲要可以入到啲咩CIVIL SURVEY嗰啲，有時都睇到我谷鬼氣<br />\n最後大技，POLY有啲BD讀，收分低撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過佢地先係真正嘅神科，因為入到去你可以無條件揀你想入嘅科（當然嗰科所屬既DEPT要同個BD一樣）<br />\n係咪即刻生命滿希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b730c3035e6c1b31344e8f54890eaa6f36f7769b","tid":159921,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:55:12.000Z","msg":"I 大 I 大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0dde45e058e417de3db48e791ed30f08b244f6","tid":159921,"uid":89729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:55:30.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"fd99cf07e6fde8b169163a8e6c9dbf007c54aa3e","tid":159921,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T10:59:15.000Z","msg":"今年CU engine 20分都入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒左DSE都唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e52eccd39dbc5d77e8442138908ba4e6a3ebf16","tid":159921,"uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年CU engine 20分都入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒左DSE都唔驚<img src=\"/a